item.title: [HIVE-9443] ORC PPD - fix fuzzy case evaluation of IS_NULL
item.description:
CLEAR LIBRARY CACHE

ORC PPD returns IS_NULL wrong for the fuzz case of some-nulls.

The code-flow in effect should be

if (min == null) {
  // all nulls
  return YES;
} else {
  if (hasNull == true) {
     // some nulls
     return YES_NO; //maybe
  }
  // no nulls
  return NO;
}
item.summary: ORC PPD - fix fuzzy case evaluation of IS_NULL
